14:58.865 --> 15:00.331
He never deserved you.

15:00.333 --> 15:01.232
He's a son of a bitch.

15:01.234 --> 15:05.136
Oh, Cleveland, you don't know
your father as well as I do.

15:05.138 --> 15:08.172
Whenever I needed something
fixed around the house,

15:08.174 --> 15:08.940
